subject: Tennis
Bees
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: For Venus Williams, there’s not much joking on the court these days. And even as the U.S. Open crowd broke out in giggles when a bee disturbed her match, Williams stood stonefaced waiting to return a serve.
